node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Jaden Smith on September 17, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'Why Psilocybin? feel like huoom connect me with myself and allow me to dive deeper into my emotions my shoe poking my heel and can smell smoke the wind, the sunset was so long ago but we're still here| can feel the thoughts the person standing next me as the stars interrupt our conversation my mind drifts towards you, an unfortunate habit of mine.'.
